</ul>
<h2>Minors</h2>
<ul>
	<li><a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/liberal-arts-sciences/phys/minor-phys/">Minor in Physics</a></li>
	<li><a href="/ucat/colleges-depts/liberal-arts-sciences/phys/minor-teaching-phys/">Minor in the Teaching of Physics</a> (suspended effective Fall 2015)</li>
