Selected topics of current interest in Physics.  Course Information:  May be repeated.  Prerequisite(s):  <a href="/search/?P=PHYS%20215" title="PHYS 215" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'PHYS 215');">PHYS 215</a> and sophomore standing or above; or approval of the department.<br/>
